 No, that's the exact wrong thing.

34:03.980 --> 34:05.660
 If you're going to use blue blockers,

34:05.660 --> 34:06.540
 we can talk about that.

34:06.540 --> 34:09.380
 That should be reserved for late in the evening

34:09.380 --> 34:12.660
