 And so you can think that you're not getting much sunlight,

36:24.420 --> 36:26.040
 but you're actually getting much more outside.

36:26.040 --> 36:28.260
 So get outside, get that sunlight early in the day

36:28.260 --> 36:30.200
 and try and do it on a consistent basis.

